sequenceDiagram
    actor Client
    participant API as Spring Boot
    participant DB as MySQL

    Note over Client,DB: Login

    Client->>API: POST /api/auth/login (username + password)
    API->>DB: SELECT user WHERE username=?
    alt User not found or disabled
        API-->>Client: 400 Bad Request
    end
    API->>API: BCrypt.matches(rawPassword, storedHash)
    alt Password wrong
        API-->>Client: 400 Invalid credentials
    end
    API->>API: JWT.sign(username, role, exp=24h, HMAC-SHA256)
    API-->>Client: 200 OK — Bearer token

    Note over Client,DB: Authenticated request (e.g. document upload)

    Client->>API: POST /api/documents/upload — Authorization: Bearer token
    API->>API: JwtAuthenticationFilter — extract + validate token
    alt Invalid or expired token
        API-->>Client: 401 Unauthorized
    end
    API->>API: Set SecurityContext (username, ROLE_ADMIN)
    API->>API: hasRole(ADMIN) check
    alt Insufficient role
        API-->>Client: 403 Forbidden
    end
    API-->>Client: 200 OK

    Note over Client,DB: Public endpoint — no token needed

    Client->>API: POST /api/chat/stream
    Note over API: /api/chat/** is permitAll() — filter skips auth
    API-->>Client: SSE stream begins
